    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Clay possessing a high absorptive capacity; it is extensively used as an absorbent in refining and decolorizing oil and fat.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
